summary:
Proven track record of outstanding flexibility, inter-personal communication skills and abstract-level process assessment. Well versed, yet able to explain complex concepts using easy to digest metaphors. Can naturally handle multiple tasks simultaneously, yet very precise while deep-diving a single point of interest. Certified in education, engineering and scientific writing. I do best in engaging, dynamic environments.

As a behavioural expert, I am constantly aware of my surroundings and analytical of social behaviour, no matter the context. Keen to be a person of trust, experience in coaching and education helps others to easily gravitate towards me. As an engineer, I dive head-first into problems to entangle the abstract systemic properties that require most attention. I deliver quality over quantity.
